The shootings in El Paso and Dayton are acts of pure evil. We mourn the lives tragically lost, and my prayers are with the victims, their families, and the first responders who rushed to help.

Since President Trump took office, the Senate has confirmed:

0⃣2⃣ Supreme Court Justices
4⃣3⃣ Appellate Court Judges 
9⃣9⃣ District Court Judges

That’s 144 strong, qualified judges confirmed to the federal bench to preserve the rule of law and uphold our Constitution.
